1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,060
(The following content may not be
suitable for viewers under 15.)

2
00:00:02,060 --> 00:00:04,040
(Viewer discretion is advised.)

3
00:00:09,160 --> 00:00:10,160
Your hair...

4
00:00:12,510 --> 00:00:14,420
Hey. Son Jin.

5
00:00:15,220 --> 00:00:17,990
Dong Moon. What are you doing here?

6
00:00:22,860 --> 00:00:25,790
- Hypocrite.
- What? Hypocrite?

7
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:36,200
Hey, what is that?

8
00:00:44,210 --> 00:00:46,050
Hey. Hold on.

9
00:00:46,050 --> 00:00:47,680
Hey. Stop.

10
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:50,120
Dong Moon.

11
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:52,090
Dong Moon, stop.

12
00:00:57,090 --> 00:00:58,090
Look.

13
00:00:59,090 --> 00:01:01,030
Don't you dare come onto Jung Hee again.

14
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:04,030
I really won't forgive you.

15
00:01:05,270 --> 00:01:07,130
Got it?

16
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:10,300
Dong Moon.

17
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,310
What are you doing here?

18
00:01:13,010 --> 00:01:14,010
What?

19
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:17,380
- You again?
- Did you follow me here?

20
00:01:19,210 --> 00:01:20,580
That's not it.

21
00:01:20,580 --> 00:01:22,680
I wasn't following you, I...

22
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:24,890
- Jung Hee!
- Number three.

23
00:01:24,890 --> 00:01:26,720
We're in trouble. You need to go home.

24
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:28,120
What is it?

25
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:31,160
Bong Soo is about to die.

26
00:01:31,690 --> 00:01:32,690
What?

27
00:01:34,830 --> 00:01:36,560
You call yourself a human being?

28
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:39,900
Are you really my one and only son?

29
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,200
After all I did to get here,

30
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:45,010
how could my only son be so pathetic?

31
00:01:45,010 --> 00:01:48,240
Whom can I live for? I should just die.

32
00:01:48,340 --> 00:01:50,210
- Get up!
- Mr. Lee.

33
00:01:50,210 --> 00:01:53,280
Why are you doing this
so early in the morning?

34
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:55,480
Your son needs to go to school.

35
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:57,820
School? He doesn't need school.

36
00:01:58,450 --> 00:02:01,120
Are you even paying attention to your son?

37
00:02:01,290 --> 00:02:03,360
You don't know if he is
at the study room...

38
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:06,530
or hanging out at some random place.

39
00:02:07,130 --> 00:02:08,930
You call yourself a mom?

40
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,930
I'm a moron.

41
00:02:11,230 --> 00:02:13,700
I'm not a mom. I'm a moron. So what?

42
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:15,770
Okay. So stay out of it.

43
00:02:15,770 --> 00:02:19,240
Stand. Stand straight!
I'll break your fingers!

44
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:22,180
- Stand.
- Stop it!

45
00:02:22,180 --> 00:02:24,380
Stop hitting him!

46
00:02:25,380 --> 00:02:26,410
Father.

47
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:30,580
Where are you coming from?

48
00:02:31,050 --> 00:02:34,090
Did you take away his
pass to the study room?

49
00:02:34,090 --> 00:02:35,820
I didn't take it away.

50
00:02:35,890 --> 00:02:37,490
He told me to go...

51
00:02:37,490 --> 00:02:39,590
That's because he's immature.

52
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:41,330
How could you take it?

53
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:45,430
How dare a chick stay out all night?

54
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:47,940
It's not like I was playing.

55
00:02:47,940 --> 00:02:50,300
- I was studying.
- What?

56
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:52,710
So why did you send only
him to a study room,

57
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:54,080
and not me?

58
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,940
What did you just say?

59
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:59,380
- Stop it.
- I told you...

60
00:02:59,380 --> 00:03:01,950
to be grateful I sent you to school.

61
00:03:01,950 --> 00:03:03,250
How dare you...

62
00:03:03,620 --> 00:03:04,650
Get over here.

63
00:03:04,820 --> 00:03:06,590
Stand right here. Now.

64
00:03:06,590 --> 00:03:07,590
No!

65
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:09,420
- I did nothing wrong.
- What?

66
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:12,590
Don't take out your anger
at Bong Soon on me.

67
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:14,060
Lee Jung Hee. Where are you going?

68
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:16,130
Stop right there! Get over here!

69
00:03:16,130 --> 00:03:17,600
Get over here.

70
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,070
- Stop it.
- Get over here.

71
00:03:19,070 --> 00:03:20,130
No!

72
00:03:20,130 --> 00:03:22,370
I have no reason to be hit
and did nothing wrong!

73
00:03:22,370 --> 00:03:24,740
- Don't do this.
- Move, will you?

74
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:27,380
- Open the door. Now!
- Father.

75
00:03:27,810 --> 00:03:29,380
Open the door right now!

76
00:03:29,380 --> 00:03:30,440
Why you...

77
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:32,650
Open the door before I break it down!

78
00:03:32,650 --> 00:03:34,450
Father, please!

79
00:03:34,450 --> 00:03:37,050
I was wrong! Hit me instead!

80
00:03:37,180 --> 00:03:39,690
What if our Bong Soo dies?

81
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:41,620
- Move.
- Oh no.

82
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:43,490
I'm sorry, Father!

83
00:03:43,490 --> 00:03:44,490
Let go.

84
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:49,430
You brat!

85
00:03:49,700 --> 00:03:51,700
Let's go die together!

86
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,900
- Let's die.
- Mom!

87
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:58,770
Let's die. Let's die together!

88
00:03:59,210 --> 00:04:01,040
- What are you doing?
- Let's die!

89
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,240
- Stop it.
- You useless...

90
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,910
If you were going to be treated like trash,

91
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:08,420
you should've died in my belly!

92
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:10,620
Why were you even born?

93
00:04:10,620 --> 00:04:13,190
You're nothing but a pain in the neck!

94
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:14,460
Die.

95
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:16,390
- Let's die together.
- I said to stop!

96
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:17,930
- Die!
- Stop it!

97
00:04:18,490 --> 00:04:22,030
I know that's targeted at me, okay?

98
00:04:22,330 --> 00:04:23,430
It's all my fault.

99
00:04:23,860 --> 00:04:25,500
I'm a loser. Happy?

100
00:04:25,870 --> 00:04:26,970
That's enough.

101
00:04:28,370 --> 00:04:29,500
Father!

102
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:33,040
Jung Hee, are you okay?

103
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,180
What is this?

104
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,600
Why are you lying down in here?

105
00:05:04,110 --> 00:05:07,140
Does it hurt? Your back.

106
00:05:07,170 --> 00:05:08,610
It doesn't hurt at all.

107
00:05:08,980 --> 00:05:11,150
I've been hit by you too many times.

108
00:05:12,810 --> 00:05:15,650
Don't you have any fears?

109
00:05:15,650 --> 00:05:18,890
How can you spend a night
where it's full of boys?

110
00:05:24,530 --> 00:05:25,730
Don't worry.

111
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:28,200
I won't go there starting today.

112
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:31,200
Jung Hee.

113
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,940
I made breakfast at the factory.

114
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:36,900
- Eat it.
- That's okay.

115
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,310
I'm just going to go.

116
00:05:38,410 --> 00:05:40,740
Eat it before you go.

117
00:05:40,910 --> 00:05:42,010
Forget it.

118
00:05:42,110 --> 00:05:43,880
Eat it.

119
00:05:45,110 --> 00:05:47,450
You got a beating so early in the morning.

120
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:50,280
You must be exhausted.

121
00:05:57,690 --> 00:05:59,660
Did Dong Moon come all the way here?

122
00:06:00,130 --> 00:06:02,300
Yes. He was worried about you.

123
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,730
He's so nosy.

124
00:06:05,570 --> 00:06:07,030
Did Bong Soo...

125
00:06:07,770 --> 00:06:08,970
get beat a lot?

126
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:13,410
Yes. He probably can't walk ever again.

127
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:14,940
Really?

128
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,710
He can't walk?

129
00:06:19,410 --> 00:06:20,450
Oh no.

130
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:33,830
Stay still, will you?

131
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:36,430
It hurts so much. Are
you trying to kill me?

132
00:06:37,730 --> 00:06:39,300
Did you get caught...

133
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:42,370
- reading comic books?
- Yes.

134
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:46,940
How did my dad know? No one knows about it.

135
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:49,640
He's like a Japanese policeman.

136
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,950
It's all your fault.

137
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:53,750
Jung Hee got hit because of you too.

138
00:06:55,050 --> 00:06:57,690
Hey! Why did you hit me there?

139
00:07:00,090 --> 00:07:01,260
What happened?

140
00:07:02,890 --> 00:07:04,590
- Salute.
- Is Jung Hee okay?

141
00:07:04,590 --> 00:07:06,530
Yes, she's fine, but I'm not...

142
00:07:06,530 --> 00:07:08,030
Why are you asking?

143
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,260
What?

144
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:26,650
Bae Dong Moon. Have you been training?

145
00:07:26,650 --> 00:07:28,450
I told you, haven't I?

146
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:31,550
Please be clear about how you act.

147
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:35,290
- You said you like her?
- Yes.

148
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:39,490
Whenever she's about to find peace,

149
00:07:39,730 --> 00:07:41,460
- you keep on...
- Dong Moon.

150
00:07:42,930 --> 00:07:44,500
That's not how you love someone.

151
00:07:45,570 --> 00:07:47,200
- Pardon?
- It's not love...

152
00:07:47,770 --> 00:07:49,000
just because you like someone.

153
00:07:51,370 --> 00:07:52,940
You should look at the other person.

154
00:07:53,540 --> 00:07:57,010
If they don't want you,
you should step back.

155
00:07:58,410 --> 00:07:59,550
That's love.

156
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,050
Is that why...

157
00:08:02,850 --> 00:08:04,620
you're watching Hae Joo...

158
00:08:06,490 --> 00:08:07,960
from a distance?

159
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,130
She won't budge,

160
00:08:16,460 --> 00:08:18,330
so you're avoiding her
because of your pride.

161
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:25,270
You're pretty daring.

162
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:28,280
I'll be open with you.

163
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:32,410
You're nothing to Jung Hee.

164
00:08:32,610 --> 00:08:35,150
That's why you should
stop being pathetic...

165
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,550
and give up what you can't have.

166
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:42,590
You'll be late. Go in.

167
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:47,290
It's not right to give up...

168
00:08:49,700 --> 00:08:51,100
just because it's not easy.

169
00:08:53,470 --> 00:08:54,770
Also,

170
00:08:55,170 --> 00:08:57,470
how are you so sure if I really am...

171
00:08:58,510 --> 00:08:59,970
a nobody to her...

172
00:09:00,710 --> 00:09:03,210
or if I'll become someone?

173
00:09:07,780 --> 00:09:08,850
I like that.

174
00:09:09,620 --> 00:09:11,290
You're optimistic.

175
00:09:13,650 --> 00:09:14,760
Good luck.

176
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:25,000
Dong Moon, you're really something.

177
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:31,570
When can I have a presence like him?

178
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:34,080
No, you did well.

179
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,740
Come here. Good job.

180
00:09:38,710 --> 00:09:39,850
Park Hae Joo's dad...

181
00:09:40,410 --> 00:09:42,180
- is a communist?
- Yes.

182
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:46,120
As far as we know, he was
a professor in Seoul.

183
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:48,090
He's taking a year off for his break.

184
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:51,160
It's not a break, he was fired.

185
00:09:51,330 --> 00:09:53,260
He commented on the current situation,

186
00:09:53,260 --> 00:09:55,760
and helped the students that protested.

187
00:09:59,470 --> 00:10:00,670
This is what happened.

188
00:10:01,540 --> 00:10:03,040
Write this down.

189
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:24,330
Park Hae Joo.

190
00:10:26,230 --> 00:10:27,290
Park Hae Joo.

191
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:28,900
Hey.

192
00:10:31,370 --> 00:10:32,400
Yes.

193
00:10:33,970 --> 00:10:35,370
Is your father doing well?

194
00:10:37,140 --> 00:10:38,210
Pardon?

195
00:10:44,450 --> 00:10:45,480
Yes.

196
00:10:57,930 --> 00:10:59,460
Did you watch the television yesterday?

197
00:10:59,460 --> 00:11:01,060
Yoon Seul was on.

198
00:11:01,330 --> 00:11:03,030
Of course I saw it.

199
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:06,000
How can someone be so handsome?

200
00:11:06,330 --> 00:11:08,300
Wait. Hae Joo.

201
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,940
You're on the day show today.

202
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:12,640
You have to eat your lunch fast.

203
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:18,710
- That's right.
- What about lunch?

204
00:11:19,180 --> 00:11:20,450
I don't feel like eating.

205
00:11:26,220 --> 00:11:27,290
Ki Ryuh.

206
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,690
This is all I could bring.

207
00:11:30,930 --> 00:11:32,930
- I'm sorry.
- Thank you.

208
00:11:36,030 --> 00:11:38,770
She doesn't pack lunch these days.

209
00:11:39,970 --> 00:11:41,300
She brings me this.

210
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:42,400
Why not?

211
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:43,800
I don't know.

212
00:11:45,070 --> 00:11:46,710
She must have a lot on her mind.

213
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:49,640
JHBS.

214
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:52,010
Jeonghyeon Girls High broadcasting service.

215
00:11:52,010 --> 00:11:54,020
We'll now begin our day show.

216
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:56,620
Hello, fellow students.

217
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,720
- Nice.
- Long time no see.

218
00:11:59,220 --> 00:12:01,590
- Did you hear a magpie...
- I have a favor to ask.

219
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:04,590
Cry on your way to school today?

220
00:12:04,590 --> 00:12:06,490
I don't know him.

221
00:12:06,890 --> 00:12:09,730
They say it means the one
you're waiting for...

222
00:12:09,730 --> 00:12:12,230
- will come back.
- If you see him...

223
00:12:12,730 --> 00:12:15,700
I hope the person you're waiting for...

224
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:22,810
will come back too.

225
00:12:24,310 --> 00:12:26,480
I'll play the first song.

226
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:30,050
Paul Anka's "Papa".

227
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:41,600
Hae Joo, that man will stay with us.

228
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:44,900
You can't tell anyone about it.

229
00:13:00,410 --> 00:13:02,180
I'm okay.

230
00:13:04,820 --> 00:13:05,890
Let's eat.

231
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:08,190
I haven't eaten yet either.

232
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:28,610
Did something happen at home?

233
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:37,850
This is good.

234
00:13:38,850 --> 00:13:41,390
- Thank you.
- Don't lie.

235
00:13:42,060 --> 00:13:43,960
You're hardly eating anything.

236
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:00,110
Please give me a box of pads.

237
00:14:07,350 --> 00:14:09,780
Did Hae Joo eat your lunch?

238
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:14,960
She picked on it. She didn't want to eat.

239
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:17,490
She wouldn't tell me what's going on.

240
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:20,260
Could it be because of Jin?

241
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,260
It's not like that.

242
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:36,640
Eng Cho, let's do a good job.

243
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:38,050
Don't worry.

244
00:14:38,710 --> 00:14:40,110
You're so cute.

245
00:14:40,410 --> 00:14:41,820
Go in.

246
00:14:44,190 --> 00:14:46,550
Hey, sister. It's me.

247
00:14:46,550 --> 00:14:48,920
Hae Joo. Hae Joo.

248
00:14:55,830 --> 00:14:57,060
Eng Cho.

249
00:14:58,130 --> 00:14:59,370
Have you been well?

250
00:14:59,830 --> 00:15:03,900
Hae Joo, do you have any food at home?

251
00:15:04,610 --> 00:15:06,870
Did you skip your meal?

252
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:11,050
Young Choon...

253
00:15:11,050 --> 00:15:14,150
is too busy to make me food.

254
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:15,750
Is that so?

255
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:28,000
Let's go inside. I'll make you food.

256
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:29,260
Okay.

257
00:15:31,570 --> 00:15:32,570
Good luck.

258
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,040
Enjoy.

259
00:15:44,650 --> 00:15:45,810
No.

260
00:15:46,010 --> 00:15:49,150
If you won't eat, I won't eat either.

261
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:53,350
Let's take turns having a spoonful.

262
00:15:53,690 --> 00:15:54,890
Okay?

263
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:59,330
Is that what Young Choon told you to do?

264
00:15:59,330 --> 00:16:00,330
Yes.

265
00:16:04,670 --> 00:16:05,670
Fine.

266
00:16:07,470 --> 00:16:08,770
I'll have a bite first.

267
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:18,150
One for you.

268
00:16:24,620 --> 00:16:25,620
Is it good?

269
00:16:25,820 --> 00:16:26,820
Yes.

270
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:46,070
What's the use?

271
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:48,740
I'm only agonized.

272
00:16:51,050 --> 00:16:53,110
It was only a dream.

273
00:16:57,990 --> 00:17:00,390
Mom, can't you knock?

274
00:17:06,430 --> 00:17:07,460
What?

275
00:17:07,460 --> 00:17:09,300
Why aren't you going out to study...

276
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:10,730
dressed like you're a guy?

277
00:17:12,530 --> 00:17:14,240
I told you I won't go.

278
00:17:14,840 --> 00:17:16,670
How can I go to a study room?

279
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:23,510
Go.

280
00:17:29,220 --> 00:17:30,350
It's okay.

281
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:32,450
I don't want Dad to beat me.

282
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:34,820
I'll get beat instead of you.

283
00:17:35,890 --> 00:17:38,730
If you talked back to your Dad,

284
00:17:38,730 --> 00:17:41,030
then show him some results.

285
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:43,760
However, don't stay up all night.

286
00:17:44,070 --> 00:17:46,270
Come back before curfew with Bong Soo.

287
00:17:47,130 --> 00:17:49,270
How can a girl stay out all night?

288
00:17:52,110 --> 00:17:54,840
Hey, pack some snacks for Jung Hee!

289
00:17:55,610 --> 00:17:57,510
Yes, ma'am.

290
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:14,260
(Study Room)

291
00:18:18,170 --> 00:18:19,330
Right, it's not this way.

292
00:18:21,900 --> 00:18:22,900
Jung Hee.

293
00:18:24,870 --> 00:18:25,870
Jin.

294
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:30,280
Are you not studying here tonight?

295
00:18:32,380 --> 00:18:35,180
I just registered for the girls' room.

296
00:18:35,780 --> 00:18:36,780
Did you?

297
00:18:38,520 --> 00:18:41,820
Come see me on the roof in about two hours.

298
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:44,260
- Pardon?
- I have something.

299
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:46,360
Okay.

300
00:18:51,770 --> 00:18:53,470
Jung Hee,

301
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,870
