302
00:19:08,750 --> 00:19:10,280
Two hours later?

303
00:19:27,670 --> 00:19:29,200
(Two hours later)

304
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:30,840
Two hours later, rooftop.

305
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:32,710
Jin and Jung Hee will meet.

306
00:19:44,550 --> 00:19:45,620
Here you go.

307
00:19:45,620 --> 00:19:46,850
Have a good night.

308
00:19:47,820 --> 00:19:49,320
- Take care.
- Goodnight.

309
00:19:49,320 --> 00:19:50,320
Bye.

310
00:19:53,860 --> 00:19:55,100
Thank you.

311
00:19:59,600 --> 00:20:00,600
Eng Cho.

312
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,700
She wouldn't know even
if she was kidnapped.

313
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:04,840
Let her sleep.

314
00:20:05,770 --> 00:20:07,880
Give her to me. I'll put her in the room.

315
00:20:09,810 --> 00:20:10,880
Eng Cho.

316
00:20:17,450 --> 00:20:18,520
Hey...

317
00:20:19,820 --> 00:20:22,990
My friend runs a pool
hall near the university.

318
00:20:24,230 --> 00:20:25,790
I asked him...

319
00:20:26,530 --> 00:20:27,900
to look for your father.

320
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:30,800
Thank you, mister...

321
00:20:32,970 --> 00:20:34,100
Thank you.

322
00:20:34,870 --> 00:20:36,140
Don't thank me.

323
00:20:36,770 --> 00:20:37,940
I didn't do anything.

324
00:20:45,650 --> 00:20:46,750
Have this.

325
00:20:46,950 --> 00:20:48,450
I'm all right.

326
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:50,650
Have it. I already opened it.

327
00:20:55,490 --> 00:20:56,490
Okay.

328
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:09,640
Gosh.

329
00:21:19,010 --> 00:21:20,110
You should be careful.

330
00:21:35,230 --> 00:21:36,230
Here.

331
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:41,040
This is the sample test for juniors.

332
00:21:42,070 --> 00:21:43,100
Did you...

333
00:21:43,900 --> 00:21:46,340
