334
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:47,510
Yes.

335
00:21:48,080 --> 00:21:49,380
I'm not sure if it'll be helpful...

336
00:21:49,940 --> 00:21:51,410
since we go to different schools.

337
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:55,620
Thank you.

338
00:21:55,620 --> 00:21:56,880
If you have any questions,

339
00:21:57,050 --> 00:21:58,350
you can always ask me.

340
00:21:59,150 --> 00:22:00,250
Jin.

341
00:22:02,090 --> 00:22:04,390
- Why are you here?
- I registered too.

342
00:22:04,390 --> 00:22:06,160
Jin, I have a question.

343
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:07,730
Can I ask you?

344
00:22:08,730 --> 00:22:11,230
This is X.

345
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:13,200
If this happens,

346
00:22:14,040 --> 00:22:15,040
Y equals...

347
00:22:16,370 --> 00:22:17,370
Wait.

348
00:22:21,410 --> 00:22:23,040
Something looks wrong.

349
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:25,310
Maybe this workbook has an error.

350
00:22:26,080 --> 00:22:28,820
You must be right. It's probably an error.

351
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:35,290
Right. Maybe we should go like this.

352
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:38,530
This is not X.

353
00:22:38,530 --> 00:22:41,200
Take it like this, so Y....

354
00:22:41,630 --> 00:22:44,400
It's either 0 or 3.

355
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:45,670
You solved it.

356
00:22:46,130 --> 00:22:48,300
Wow, Dong Moon.

357
00:22:57,810 --> 00:22:58,980
- Dong Moon.
- Yes?

358
00:22:59,050 --> 00:23:00,850
Does it feel good to make a fool of me?

359
00:23:02,550 --> 00:23:04,650
Yes. It feels good.

360
00:23:04,650 --> 00:23:06,050
Hey.

361
00:23:15,030 --> 00:23:16,030
All right.

362
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:18,470
Today is the day.

363
00:23:18,570 --> 00:23:19,700
Keep your eyes wide open,

364
00:23:20,030 --> 00:23:23,200
and give it your best to
answer the questions.

365
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,810
Ready, start.

366
00:23:35,150 --> 00:23:38,390
Hae Joo? Isn't she the one
that came from Seoul...

367
00:23:38,390 --> 00:23:40,120
and came over to our place?

368
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:42,560
That's her. She's pretty.

369
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:46,660
And she's getting on with Young Choon?

370
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:50,160
Yes. I saw them talk in his pharmacy.

371
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:52,170
I saw it with my own eyes.

372
00:23:52,470 --> 00:23:54,340
No way.

373
00:23:54,340 --> 00:23:56,770
Young Choon has a sister
named Eng Cho, right?

374
00:23:56,770 --> 00:23:58,740
Hae Joo brought her...

375
00:23:59,410 --> 00:24:00,840
on her back like this.

376
00:24:00,840 --> 00:24:02,010
They are so in love.

377
00:24:02,010 --> 00:24:03,540
Keep on rolling my hair.

378
00:24:03,840 --> 00:24:06,110
They say it's always the quiet ones...

379
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:08,180
that make trouble.

380
00:24:10,550 --> 00:24:12,690
Jung Hee, are you going out to study?

381
00:24:12,890 --> 00:24:13,890
Yes.

382
00:24:13,990 --> 00:24:15,190
Jung Hee.

383
00:24:16,060 --> 00:24:17,060
What?

384
00:24:17,060 --> 00:24:20,830
Don't hang out with Hae Joo anymore.

385
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:22,600
She's dating Young Choon.

386
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:23,960
It's not like that.

387
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:25,600
Young Choon's sister, Eng Cho,

388
00:24:25,670 --> 00:24:27,440
seems to like Hae Joo.

389
00:24:27,670 --> 00:24:30,140
- Hae Joo is so nice.
- Gibberish.

390
00:24:30,570 --> 00:24:33,270
You need to be careful of the nice girls.

391
00:24:33,610 --> 00:24:35,980
Nice and pretty girls...

392
00:24:35,980 --> 00:24:39,850
go around stealing other people's husbands.

393
00:24:41,220 --> 00:24:43,450
- That's not right.
- It's true.

394
00:24:43,550 --> 00:24:47,020
Then Auntie must've stolen
hundreds of husbands.

395
00:24:47,190 --> 00:24:49,760
She's pretty and nice.

396
00:24:50,660 --> 00:24:52,690
- I'm not nice.
- Regardless,

397
00:24:52,790 --> 00:24:54,260
Hae Joo isn't like that.

398
00:24:54,300 --> 00:24:55,960
Don't go around saying that.

399
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:58,770
"Don't go around"? Am I your friend?

400
00:24:59,370 --> 00:25:00,740
What gibberish.

401
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:11,680
Don't hang out with that girl Hae Joo.

402
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:14,180
I hear she's dating Young Choon.

403
00:25:14,950 --> 00:25:17,750
Stupid. Just what did she do?

404
00:25:38,210 --> 00:25:39,240
Hae Joo.

405
00:25:46,080 --> 00:25:47,110
Hae Joo.

406
00:25:49,280 --> 00:25:50,790
- Jung Hee.
- Is...

407
00:25:51,550 --> 00:25:52,890
something wrong?

408
00:25:54,190 --> 00:25:56,420
Your father hasn't come home?

409
00:25:57,290 --> 00:25:58,890
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

410
00:26:00,490 --> 00:26:02,460
I just couldn't.

411
00:26:04,370 --> 00:26:05,470
Jung Hee.

412
00:26:06,130 --> 00:26:07,400
You can't...

413
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:11,140
