414
00:26:23,650 --> 00:26:24,890
What do I do?

415
00:26:26,390 --> 00:26:27,420
Jung Hee.

416
00:26:31,690 --> 00:26:32,790
Jin.

417
00:26:32,990 --> 00:26:34,300
Is something wrong?

418
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:37,130
What is it?

419
00:26:41,170 --> 00:26:42,170
Well...

420
00:26:46,340 --> 00:26:47,910
Hae Joo's father?

421
00:26:48,310 --> 00:26:52,110
I heard your father was
the chief of police.

422
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:55,020
I was wondering...

423
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:57,750
if he could help.

424
00:27:01,220 --> 00:27:03,090
Yes, sure.

425
00:27:04,060 --> 00:27:05,360
I'll ask.

426
00:27:06,230 --> 00:27:09,160
You can't tell anyone else about this,

427
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:11,470
- okay?
- Okay.

428
00:27:12,130 --> 00:27:15,370
You have to keep it a secret too.

429
00:27:16,070 --> 00:27:17,200
Okay.

430
00:27:18,810 --> 00:27:22,080
I thought that was the
best thing back then.

431
00:27:23,580 --> 00:27:26,280
I was just slightly uncomfortable...

432
00:27:26,550 --> 00:27:30,120
that Jin and Hae Joo may
see each other again...

433
00:27:30,450 --> 00:27:32,390
because of this.

434
00:27:36,890 --> 00:27:37,890
Jung Hee.

435
00:27:38,860 --> 00:27:39,990
Aren't you going to study?

436
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:42,530
- What?
- Is something wrong?

437
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:45,170
Did you bomb your test?

438
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:49,740
It'll be fine, right?

439
00:27:50,140 --> 00:27:52,110
What? What will?

440
00:27:54,140 --> 00:27:55,240
Nothing.

441
00:27:56,510 --> 00:27:57,680
You did well.

442
00:27:58,350 --> 00:28:00,380
You don't even know what it is.

443
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:03,350
Anything you do is good.

444
00:28:04,350 --> 00:28:07,360
You did a good job, Lee Jung Hee.

445
00:28:12,730 --> 00:28:14,130
Yes, hello?

446
00:28:14,530 --> 00:28:16,460
Yes. Young Choon?

447
00:28:16,900 --> 00:28:18,070
Just a minute.

448
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,870
- Is that for me?
- Here.

449
00:28:21,700 --> 00:28:22,800
Hello?

450
00:28:23,840 --> 00:28:25,140
Yes.

451
00:28:27,270 --> 00:28:28,280
What?

452
00:28:32,550 --> 00:28:33,980
Where are you going?

453
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:39,650
What? Park Jin Soo was released?

454
00:28:40,550 --> 00:28:42,190
- When?
- Park Jin Soo.

455
00:28:44,030 --> 00:28:46,190
- Hae Joo's father?
- And his guilt?

456
00:28:46,960 --> 00:28:48,030
What? Not guilty?

457
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:51,470
How could he be not guilty?

458
00:29:09,050 --> 00:29:10,480
I had no idea.

459
00:29:11,450 --> 00:29:12,550
I didn't know...

460
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:15,220
Hae Joo was having such a hard time.

461
00:29:21,730 --> 00:29:22,800
Hae Joo.

462
00:29:37,550 --> 00:29:39,480
- Which way?
- Over here.

463
00:29:50,560 --> 00:29:51,660
Can you hold him?

464
00:29:55,530 --> 00:29:56,630
Dad.

465
00:29:58,070 --> 00:29:59,100
Dad.

466
00:30:00,270 --> 00:30:02,270
What happened?

467
00:30:03,870 --> 00:30:05,440
He was passed out...

468
00:30:06,810 --> 00:30:08,240
at the bus terminal.

469
00:30:10,140 --> 00:30:11,550
Dad.

470
00:30:19,570 --> 00:30:22,810
[VIU Ver] E05 Girls' Generation
1979 "Fool in Love" -= Ruo Xi =-

471
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:31,670
Jin.

472
00:30:34,570 --> 00:30:35,700
Jung Hee.

473
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:39,570
Are you heading home?

474
00:30:43,540 --> 00:30:44,550
Yes.

475
00:30:48,250 --> 00:30:51,020
Hae Joo's father came back.

476
00:30:51,090 --> 00:30:52,190
He did?

477
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:55,490
Because you helped...

478
00:30:57,460 --> 00:30:58,460
No.

479
00:30:59,360 --> 00:31:00,430
I...

480
00:31:01,860 --> 00:31:03,630
couldn't help at all.

481
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:10,970
That's right.

482
00:31:11,670 --> 00:31:13,140
Jin...

483
00:31:13,670 --> 00:31:16,440
still liked Hae Joo.

484
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:20,980
Just as I still liked him.

485
00:31:42,800 --> 00:31:44,740
Good job, everyone.

486
00:31:53,280 --> 00:31:55,020
Exams are finally over.

487
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:56,550
Freedom!

488
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:59,090
Should we go watch a movie today?

489
00:31:59,220 --> 00:32:01,860
Sounds good. Jung Hee, go with us.

490
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,990
No. I want to rest.

491
00:32:04,760 --> 00:32:05,960
Brat.

492
00:32:06,130 --> 00:32:07,930
You stayed up all night again, didn't you?

493
00:32:08,300 --> 00:32:11,000
You'll become the top student at that rate.

494
00:32:12,770 --> 00:32:15,170
What? Hae Joo is the top student.

495
00:32:15,670 --> 00:32:16,740
Look.

496
00:32:16,840 --> 00:32:20,040
She's exhausted from studying all night.

497
00:32:21,180 --> 00:32:22,940
She didn't study all night.

498
00:32:24,650 --> 00:32:27,620
This morning, my mom saw...

499
00:32:27,850 --> 00:32:30,890
Young Choon leave Hae Joo's house.

500
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:33,020
Really?

501
00:32:33,150 --> 00:32:34,790
What do you mean?

502
00:32:35,220 --> 00:32:37,830
Hey. Get your mom glasses.

503
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:40,030
No, it's true.

504
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:41,930
- It is not.
- It is too.

505
00:32:44,530 --> 00:32:46,070
This is better.

506
00:32:46,670 --> 00:32:47,840
This is number two.

507
00:32:58,550 --> 00:33:00,480
- Hae Joo.
- Hey.

508
00:33:01,450 --> 00:33:02,780
Did you do well on the exam?

509
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:05,250
Yes. Sort of.

510
00:33:07,190 --> 00:33:10,620
My dad came home.

511
00:33:12,690 --> 00:33:15,030
Really? That's great.

512
00:33:15,530 --> 00:33:16,800
That's really great.

513
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,000
What?

514
00:33:21,700 --> 00:33:24,440
Is something else wrong?

515
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:30,280
No.

516
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:33,610
Thanks for worrying.

517
00:33:46,930 --> 00:33:48,630
- A thug?
- Yes.

518
00:33:50,600 --> 00:33:53,930
Every thug in Daegu knows Young Choon.

519
00:33:54,600 --> 00:33:56,670
That little scumbag.

520
00:33:56,670 --> 00:33:57,710
I know!

521
00:33:58,110 --> 00:33:59,440
That isn't all.

522
00:33:59,440 --> 00:34:02,510
You know that little girl,
supposedly his sister?

523
00:34:02,640 --> 00:34:05,150
- Yes.
- That kid...

524
00:34:09,250 --> 00:34:11,450
- What is it?
- They say she's his kid.

525
00:34:16,860 --> 00:34:18,030
Hello.

526
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:25,800
You know me, right?

527
00:34:28,200 --> 00:34:29,440
I know...

528
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,470
you helped Hae Joo.

529
00:34:33,740 --> 00:34:34,880
Thank you.

530
00:34:35,640 --> 00:34:38,280
But I'd like you to be more careful...

531
00:34:38,380 --> 00:34:40,150
about what people may think.

532
00:34:41,020 --> 00:34:42,180
What people may think?

533
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,260
Not what you think?

534
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:54,560
- That's not it.
- I hear...

535
00:34:54,560 --> 00:34:56,160
you're the police chief's son.

536
00:34:58,730 --> 00:35:00,570
Can the police chief's son...

537
00:35:00,940 --> 00:35:02,700
meet with a thug like me...

538
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:05,270
in public like this?

539
00:35:06,610 --> 00:35:07,610
Can you?

540
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:13,980
So many people can see.

541
00:35:21,120 --> 00:35:22,220
Hey, kid.

542
00:35:23,120 --> 00:35:25,560
Don't act tough in front of me,

543
00:35:26,290 --> 00:35:27,900
and go home and study.

544
00:35:50,050 --> 00:35:51,050
Hae Joo.

545
00:35:52,190 --> 00:35:54,820
I hear Young Choon is a thug.

546
00:35:54,820 --> 00:35:55,820
He hangs out with...

547
00:35:55,820 --> 00:35:57,930
Young Choon isn't like that.

548
00:35:59,460 --> 00:36:00,730
He helped me a lot...

549
00:36:01,460 --> 00:36:02,760
when things were tough for me.

550
00:36:03,630 --> 00:36:04,770
That's because...

551
00:36:05,170 --> 00:36:06,500
he had bad intentions toward you.

552
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:07,840
He really...

553
00:36:08,600 --> 00:36:09,740
isn't like that.

554
00:36:15,140 --> 00:36:16,380
He is...

555
00:36:17,510 --> 00:36:18,580
a good person.

556
00:36:26,120 --> 00:36:27,250
I really...

557
00:36:29,260 --> 00:36:31,090
mean nothing to you...

558
00:36:33,330 --> 00:36:34,400
even now.

559
00:36:53,310 --> 00:36:54,450
- Father.
- You.

560
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:56,320
I told you...

561
00:36:56,350 --> 00:36:59,590
not to do anything to destroy my life!

562
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:02,820
Why do you keep going to
that communist's house?

563
00:37:02,860 --> 00:37:04,760
If you keep disobeying me,

564
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:07,060
I can take extreme measures.

565
00:37:07,430 --> 00:37:08,530
Understand?

566
00:37:15,240 --> 00:37:17,740
We have the results of the midterms.

567
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:21,240
I actually expected...

568
00:37:22,080 --> 00:37:23,680
great things from you.

569
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:26,310
I was a stupid pig, a rat.

570
00:37:26,980 --> 00:37:31,090
Once again, our class, without fail,

571
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:33,490
came in last.

572
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:38,660
Funny, right, punk?

573
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:42,530
There was one girl...

574
00:37:43,730 --> 00:37:47,570
who disappointed me like crazy.

575
00:37:47,570 --> 00:37:48,640
Her name is...

576
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,570
Why you little...

577
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,210
Hae Joo.

578
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:03,480
- Hey, Hae Joo.
- Yes?

579
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:06,150
Did you cheat at your old school?

580
00:38:06,750 --> 00:38:08,790
How could the top scorer in the country...

581
00:38:08,790 --> 00:38:11,690
not make top 30 in this stupid class?

582
00:38:11,690 --> 00:38:12,690
- What?
- What?

583
00:38:12,690 --> 00:38:14,500
- Really?
- What?

584
00:38:14,500 --> 00:38:15,800
Oh, my gosh.

585
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:20,840
There is...

586
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,510
one person...

587
00:38:24,570 --> 00:38:27,740
who provided me a sliver of comfort.

588
00:38:27,740 --> 00:38:28,740
Her name is...

589
00:38:30,180 --> 00:38:31,180
Jung Hee.

590
00:38:34,950 --> 00:38:37,520
Jung Hee went up...

591
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:39,720
a whopping 230 spots.

592
00:38:40,050 --> 00:38:42,990
And came in seventh in our class.

593
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:45,760
- Wow.
- Nice.

594
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:46,760
Seriously...

595
00:38:48,030 --> 00:38:51,170
Anyway, you should give
congratulations when due.

596
00:38:51,570 --> 00:38:54,100
Okay. Let's give Jung Hee
a round of applause.

597
00:39:05,110 --> 00:39:06,110
What's this?

598
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:13,790
Seventh? Seventh in your class?

599
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:16,560
You brat.

600
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:17,990
You faked this!

601
00:39:17,990 --> 00:39:20,860
I did not. Ask my homeroom teacher.

602
00:39:22,730 --> 00:39:23,860
Hey!

603
00:39:24,430 --> 00:39:26,730
Jung Hee came in seventh! Seventh!

604
00:39:26,730 --> 00:39:28,070
Oh my gosh!

605
00:39:28,300 --> 00:39:31,040
- Where?
- Look here. Seventh.

606
00:39:32,240 --> 00:39:35,010
Jung Hee. You did great.

607
00:39:37,650 --> 00:39:38,680
What's this?

608
00:39:42,820 --> 00:39:44,520
Father, did you see?

609
00:39:44,820 --> 00:39:46,790
I can do well too.

610
00:39:48,620 --> 00:39:50,990
Bong Soo. What did you place?

611
00:39:53,430 --> 00:39:54,630
Tell me.

612
00:39:55,100 --> 00:39:58,230
The same as before.

613
00:39:58,530 --> 00:39:59,600
The same?

614
00:40:00,770 --> 00:40:02,170
Then 40...

615
00:40:02,270 --> 00:40:04,310
Why you little...

616
00:40:04,310 --> 00:40:07,380
Come on. Calm down.

617
00:40:07,380 --> 00:40:11,450
First, you should compliment Jung Hee.

618
00:40:11,450 --> 00:40:13,110
We never had...

619
00:40:13,110 --> 00:40:15,920
anyone who did this well in school before.

620
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:19,290
You loser. You're worse than a girl.

621
00:40:19,590 --> 00:40:20,820
Darn it.

622
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,390
Father!

623
00:40:23,620 --> 00:40:24,630
What?

624
00:40:24,630 --> 00:40:27,330
Why won't you compliment me?

625
00:40:27,560 --> 00:40:28,560
Good job.

626
00:40:29,230 --> 00:40:31,900
Wait. Since I did well,

627
00:40:32,700 --> 00:40:34,040
I want a gift.

628
00:40:34,100 --> 00:40:35,670
Don't be stupid.

629
00:40:35,670 --> 00:40:37,100
- Here, here.
- Forget it.

630
00:40:37,100 --> 00:40:38,470
Not money.

631
00:40:39,070 --> 00:40:40,240
Then what?

632
00:40:40,980 --> 00:40:42,180
From now on,

633
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:44,150
treat me the same...

634
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:46,080
as Bong Soo.

635
00:40:47,820 --> 00:40:50,020
Instead of saying, "a girl' this,

636
00:40:50,620 --> 00:40:51,950
"a girl" that.

637
00:40:52,190 --> 00:40:54,520
Has this girl gone insane?

638
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:57,830
You should feel bad for
discouraging Bong Soo.

639
00:41:00,230 --> 00:41:01,600
Father!

640
00:41:02,330 --> 00:41:03,800
You brat.

641
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:07,170
Why did you ruin it after working so hard?

642
00:41:07,170 --> 00:41:10,000
Here. Here. Take this.

643
00:41:11,770 --> 00:41:12,910
Take this!

644
00:41:12,910 --> 00:41:14,640
Shall I bring it to her?

645
00:41:15,110 --> 00:41:16,380
Shut it.

646
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:27,120
(Rank 7 out of 64)

647
00:41:29,460 --> 00:41:30,460
I...

648
00:41:30,990 --> 00:41:33,430
really hate my father.

649
00:41:34,730 --> 00:41:36,360
I can't stand him.

650
00:41:41,570 --> 00:41:44,940
Does it hurt that much to
compliment Jung Hee...

651
00:41:45,140 --> 00:41:46,670
for doing a good job?

652
00:41:48,210 --> 00:41:50,810
It's a given for a student
to do well in school.

653
00:41:50,810 --> 00:41:52,580
If it were Bong Soo,

654
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:55,480
you would've cooked an entire pig.

655
00:41:57,820 --> 00:41:59,750
There's no point in a girl
doing well in school.

656
00:41:59,750 --> 00:42:01,490
It'll only make her life more difficult.

657
00:42:01,490 --> 00:42:02,890
Then what?

658
00:42:03,120 --> 00:42:06,330
Am I living it up because I didn't study?

659
00:42:08,300 --> 00:42:09,800
How dare you...

660
00:42:18,340 --> 00:42:19,540
Where are you going?

661
00:42:20,370 --> 00:42:22,010
I'm going to sleep...

662
00:42:22,010 --> 00:42:24,280
with the other witch with a cruddy life.

663
00:42:31,820 --> 00:42:33,420
Darn it.

664
00:42:38,660 --> 00:42:42,730
Why did she have to get her smarts from me?

665
00:42:45,070 --> 00:42:47,540
It's cramped.

666
00:42:47,540 --> 00:42:48,740
Jung Hee.

667
00:42:52,270 --> 00:42:54,210
Want some new clothes?

668
00:42:54,480 --> 00:42:55,910
A name brand?

669
00:42:56,680 --> 00:42:57,710
Really?

670
00:42:58,110 --> 00:42:59,750
Then buy me two.

671
00:42:59,850 --> 00:43:01,450
A t-shirt and a blouse.

672
00:43:02,180 --> 00:43:03,990
Get just one, you brat.

673
00:43:10,320 --> 00:43:11,490
You did well.

674
00:43:14,460 --> 00:43:16,900
You didn't get much milk
when you were a baby...

675
00:43:16,960 --> 00:43:18,630
because of your brother,

676
00:43:18,630 --> 00:43:20,370
and were always weak.

677
00:43:20,500 --> 00:43:24,340
I wondered if you'd survive in this world.

678
00:43:24,340 --> 00:43:25,910
You did well.

679
00:43:29,210 --> 00:43:30,750
Good night.

680
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:35,550
Mom.

681
00:43:35,850 --> 00:43:36,920
What?

682
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:38,750
Give me my milk now.

683
00:43:38,750 --> 00:43:40,520
Are you insane?

684
00:43:40,520 --> 00:43:42,260
You're all grown up. Hey!

685
00:43:42,260 --> 00:43:43,390
- I want my milk.
- Let go!

686
00:43:43,390 --> 00:43:45,360
Have you lost your mind? That tickles.

687
00:44:05,980 --> 00:44:07,210
Straps?

688
00:44:07,980 --> 00:44:09,280
It's my gift to you...

689
00:44:09,520 --> 00:44:11,050
for doing well on your exams.

690
00:44:11,420 --> 00:44:13,850
Auntie. How did you know it was my dream...

691
00:44:13,850 --> 00:44:15,560
to wear a strappy undershirt?

692
00:44:16,360 --> 00:44:17,460
Do you like it?

693
00:44:18,030 --> 00:44:19,760
It's super pretty.

694
00:44:20,460 --> 00:44:21,860
Auntie!

695
00:44:26,030 --> 00:44:29,770
The police sent us this notice.

696
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:31,770
Sir.

697
00:44:33,070 --> 00:44:34,640
Even if Hae Joo's father...

698
00:44:34,910 --> 00:44:36,740
commit an act of communism...

699
00:44:36,740 --> 00:44:39,010
Not "even if". It's the truth.

700
00:44:43,350 --> 00:44:46,790
Regardless, that's an adult matter.

701
00:44:47,220 --> 00:44:48,690
What do the kids know?

702
00:44:48,690 --> 00:44:50,090
Mr. Oh.

703
00:44:50,960 --> 00:44:53,830
Don't you watch the news about North Korea?

704
00:44:54,030 --> 00:44:57,230
Communism seeps through
adults and children...

705
00:44:57,230 --> 00:45:00,700
and dyes them all red
without discrimination.

706
00:45:00,900 --> 00:45:02,100
So,

707
00:45:02,570 --> 00:45:05,670
you must record everything Hae Joo does...

708
00:45:05,670 --> 00:45:08,680
and report them to me from now on.

709
00:45:08,940 --> 00:45:10,040
Understand?

710
00:45:26,260 --> 00:45:28,430
Jung Hee. Hae Joo.

711
00:45:28,930 --> 00:45:30,830
Gwi Ja. Sit down.

712
00:45:32,200 --> 00:45:34,240
The rest of you, take the position.

713
00:45:34,800 --> 00:45:36,570
Hold the chalk and take the position.

714
00:45:37,170 --> 00:45:40,470
You agreed not to give
that punishment anymore.

715
00:45:41,480 --> 00:45:42,580
Positions.

716
00:45:42,640 --> 00:45:44,280
- Mr. Oh.
- Positions!

717
00:45:53,750 --> 00:45:54,860
Okay.

718
00:45:55,960 --> 00:45:57,190
Ready?

719
00:45:58,590 --> 00:45:59,660
Mr. Oh.

720
00:46:05,470 --> 00:46:08,900
You promised not to do this.

721
00:46:15,310 --> 00:46:16,710
When did I do that?

722
00:46:17,280 --> 00:46:19,110
You demanded it of me.

723
00:46:19,110 --> 00:46:20,820
But you said you wouldn't do it.

724
00:46:21,280 --> 00:46:24,620
- You agreed...
- I had said I wouldn't,

725
00:46:25,620 --> 00:46:28,290
but I have decided to do it again.

726
00:46:29,990 --> 00:46:31,760
To you guys...

727
00:46:32,830 --> 00:46:36,000
who maintained last place on the midterms,

728
00:46:36,330 --> 00:46:37,600
this is the only solution.

729
00:46:43,600 --> 00:46:45,470
Okay. Get ready.

730
00:46:45,710 --> 00:46:46,740
Mr. Oh.

731
00:46:48,480 --> 00:46:51,980
But still, this punishment is wrong.

732
00:47:00,890 --> 00:47:01,960
Wrong?

733
00:47:03,020 --> 00:47:06,690
It's not like you're being punished.

734
00:47:07,530 --> 00:47:08,700
Why do you care so much?

735
00:47:09,100 --> 00:47:11,000
I may not be the one being punished,

736
00:47:11,570 --> 00:47:14,300
but seeing my friends
receive such unjust...

737
00:47:14,300 --> 00:47:15,940
Just do it already.

738
00:47:20,140 --> 00:47:21,480
Ae Sook, sit down.

739
00:47:24,180 --> 00:47:25,810
The rest of you too. Sit down.

740
00:47:37,990 --> 00:47:39,530
Then today,

741
00:47:40,660 --> 00:47:42,260
your Joan of Arc,

742
00:47:43,200 --> 00:47:46,270
Hae Joo, will receive
the punishment instead.

743
00:47:47,670 --> 00:47:48,800
Step forward.

744
00:47:49,670 --> 00:47:50,970
Step forward now!

745
00:47:58,980 --> 00:48:01,580
I will take the punishment on their behalf.

746
00:48:02,180 --> 00:48:03,220
However,

747
00:48:04,190 --> 00:48:06,650
I refuse that punishment method.

748
00:48:08,990 --> 00:48:10,090
You do?

749
00:48:11,530 --> 00:48:14,360
Then will you receive any other method...

750
00:48:14,900 --> 00:48:16,060
gladly?

751
00:48:17,130 --> 00:48:18,270
Yes.

752
00:48:18,600 --> 00:48:19,630
Fine.

753
00:48:20,900 --> 00:48:22,000
Then...

754
00:48:23,200 --> 00:48:26,010
in exchange for the ones who should've...

755
00:48:26,710 --> 00:48:28,280
been punished today,

756
00:48:28,940 --> 00:48:30,180
as well as...

757
00:48:30,780 --> 00:48:33,080
for the ones who will deserve...

758
00:48:33,110 --> 00:48:34,920
the punishment going forward,

759
00:48:35,620 --> 00:48:38,150
Hae Joo will take 100 laps...

760
00:48:38,150 --> 00:48:39,450
around the yard.

761
00:48:40,720 --> 00:48:41,760
Go now!

762
00:48:43,190 --> 00:48:44,230
Mr. Oh.

763
00:48:46,430 --> 00:48:48,430
It's raining out.

764
00:48:48,600 --> 00:48:50,460
So what if it's raining?

765
00:48:51,700 --> 00:48:54,200
Do you want to run with Hae Joo?

766
00:48:55,000 --> 00:48:56,270
Anyone else?

767
00:48:56,670 --> 00:48:58,910
Anyone who agrees with Hae Joo...

768
00:48:59,210 --> 00:49:02,340
may go run with her right now!

769
00:49:03,210 --> 00:49:04,250
Anyone?

770
00:49:14,560 --> 00:49:15,560
See that?

771
00:49:17,290 --> 00:49:19,860
This is why you should know your place.

772
00:49:21,360 --> 00:49:24,400
You talk about humiliation and insult...

773
00:49:24,970 --> 00:49:27,600
to try to help these pigs here,

774
00:49:28,740 --> 00:49:32,170
but they aren't grateful to you one bit.

775
00:49:33,940 --> 00:49:35,840
This is how the world works.

776
00:49:39,910 --> 00:49:41,550
Go to the school yard now.

777
00:49:43,620 --> 00:49:44,850
Go right now!

778
00:49:56,900 --> 00:49:58,030
Mr. Oh.

779
00:49:59,870 --> 00:50:01,840
Okay. Page 63.

780
00:50:02,170 --> 00:50:03,240
Mr. Oh!

781
00:50:04,640 --> 00:50:07,510
Yes, Jung Hee. Do you have a question?

782
00:50:08,240 --> 00:50:09,910
My goodness.

783
00:50:10,410 --> 00:50:11,910
Jung Hee...

784
00:50:12,410 --> 00:50:14,950
finally became interested in studying.

785
00:50:15,150 --> 00:50:17,550
This is great. What is it?

786
00:50:17,790 --> 00:50:18,820
I'll...

787
00:50:20,090 --> 00:50:21,520
go with her.

788
00:50:23,960 --> 00:50:25,090
Where?

789
00:50:25,530 --> 00:50:27,290
Jung Hee. What are you doing?

790
00:50:29,360 --> 00:50:31,430
Jung Hee. Hey.

791
00:50:32,330 --> 00:50:34,440
Hey, Jung Hee. Jung Hee!

792
00:50:36,000 --> 00:50:37,170
Jung Hee!

793
00:50:50,950 --> 00:50:52,450
Why did you come after me?

794
00:50:53,550 --> 00:50:55,120
I didn't come after you.

795
00:50:55,960 --> 00:50:57,460
I came out because...

796
00:50:58,390 --> 00:51:00,330
I couldn't agree with Mr. Oh.

797
00:51:12,410 --> 00:51:15,610
I had hated Hae Joo again.

798
00:51:24,190 --> 00:51:27,520
I couldn't receive Jin's love...

799
00:51:27,760 --> 00:51:29,660
no matter what I did,

800
00:51:30,660 --> 00:51:33,130
but Hae Joo had it,

801
00:51:33,890 --> 00:51:35,060
so I hate her.

802
00:51:42,540 --> 00:51:43,770
However,

803
00:51:44,210 --> 00:51:46,810
I couldn't watch her...

804
00:51:50,140 --> 00:51:51,980
fight by herself.

805
00:51:55,850 --> 00:51:59,190
I have no idea why.

806
00:52:49,240 --> 00:52:50,370
Did you finish?

807
00:52:50,770 --> 00:52:51,840
Yes.

808
00:52:53,910 --> 00:52:55,210
You may go home.

809
00:53:20,770 --> 00:53:23,900
I heard you were punished.

810
00:53:27,610 --> 00:53:28,740
Why are you here?

811
00:53:29,510 --> 00:53:30,780
It's embarrassing.

812
00:53:44,430 --> 00:53:45,460
Let's go.

813
00:53:46,030 --> 00:53:47,500
You want me to use it by myself?

814
00:53:47,630 --> 00:53:51,030
What if a teacher sees
us using it together?

815
00:53:52,670 --> 00:53:53,770
Let's go.

816
00:54:00,980 --> 00:54:02,210
Share it with me.

817
00:54:04,280 --> 00:54:07,080
If I get caught, I'll
just be punished again.

818
00:54:08,220 --> 00:54:09,650
I'm not scared one bit.

819
00:54:17,390 --> 00:54:18,530
Okay.

820
00:54:19,660 --> 00:54:20,800
Let's go.

821
00:54:49,290 --> 00:54:50,390
Jung Hee.

822
00:54:50,420 --> 00:54:52,660
I meant to pick you up.

823
00:54:54,030 --> 00:54:56,300
You'll catch a cold. Take a shower.

824
00:54:58,430 --> 00:55:00,500
What's wrong? Are you hurt?

825
00:55:01,140 --> 00:55:02,170
No.

826
00:55:02,670 --> 00:55:03,740
Oh, my gosh.

827
00:55:05,640 --> 00:55:06,640
Jung Hee.

828
00:55:07,070 --> 00:55:09,640
We're friends now, right?

829
00:55:13,510 --> 00:55:16,050
Auntie. I need to step out.

830
00:55:16,620 --> 00:55:19,420
Where are you going like that? Jung Hee.

831
00:55:31,900 --> 00:55:37,570
(Pharmacy)

832
00:55:38,370 --> 00:55:40,340
I should've stayed with her.

833
00:58:20,270 --> 00:58:21,300
Don't cry.

834
00:58:55,240 --> 00:58:57,840
(Girls' Generation 1979)

835
00:59:00,810 --> 00:59:02,140
Stop following me.

836
00:59:02,610 --> 00:59:04,010
You're annoying me.

837
00:59:04,980 --> 00:59:06,710
I warned you...

838
00:59:06,850 --> 00:59:09,120
to stay away from Young Choon.

839
00:59:09,750 --> 00:59:11,320
A date? With Jin?

840
00:59:11,320 --> 00:59:13,020
They took the bus and went far, far away.

841
00:59:13,020 --> 00:59:14,920
They're very meticulous.

842
00:59:15,020 --> 00:59:16,220
Dong Moon?

843
00:59:17,330 --> 00:59:19,330
Jin is transferring to a school in Seoul.

844
00:59:21,330 --> 00:59:22,330
Then, was that...

845
00:59:22,800 --> 00:59:24,400
the last time?
